asy-to-use web interface. It widens the user base of phylogeny-aware multiple sequence alignment and allows the performance of all alignment-related activity for small sequence analysis projects using only a standard web browser.},
author = {L{\"{o}}ytynoja, Ari and Goldman, Nick},
doi = {10.1186/1471-2105-11-579},
file = {:home/MaxEmil/Documents/Mendeley{\_}DB/2010/L{\"{o}}ytynoja, Goldman{\_}2010{\_}webPRANK a phylogeny-aware multiple sequence aligner with interactive alignment browser.pdf:pdf},
isbn = {1471-2105},
